name: TimeTravel Madness
description:
You find yourself in a room whit 5 doors. 3 of them teleports you to one of the other to but 2 of them brings you back or forward in time. You can only know after you killed all enemies. Collect all 5 of the time fragments to escape from this chaos.

You can download my game for free from: https://playforwin.hu/games/timetravelmadness/
